<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset='utf-8' />
        <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
        <title>Verify Your Email - MTD Tax</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .header {
                background-color: #2563eb;
                color: white;
                padding: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            }
            .content {
                background-color: #f8fafc;
                padding: 30px;
                border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            }
            .otp-code {
                background-color: #e2e8f0;
                padding: 15px;
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: bold;
                letter-spacing: 5px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                margin: 20px 0;
                color: #1e293b;
            }
            .footer {
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 30px;
                color: #64748b;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .button {
                display: inline-block;
                background-color: #2563eb;
                color: white;
                padding: 12px 24px;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 6px;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class='header'>
            <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
            <p>Welcome to MTD Tax</p>
        </div>

        <div class='content'>
            <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>

            <p>Thank you for signing up with MTD Tax! To complete your
                registration, please verify your email address by entering the
                verification code below:</p>

            <div class='otp-code'>
                {{otp}}
            </div>

            <p><strong>This code will expire in 10 minutes.</strong></p>

            <p>If you didn't create an account with MTD Tax, please ignore this
                email.</p>

            <p>If you're having trouble with the verification code, you can
                request a new one from your account dashboard.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br />The MTD Tax Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class='footer'>
            <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 MTD Tax. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>